Text: CANCELLED ERCOT Notification Postcard Language Workshop Cc PST The workshop this Thursday has been cancelled due to scheduling conflicts with the ERCOT workshop It will be rescheduled for the week of notification of the exact timeplace will be sent out shortly Thank you for your patience Heidi Original Message From Schrab Heidi Sent Wednesday January AM To Cc Patricia Dolese Shawnee Claibornpinto Corona Connie Fenoglio Walt Briesemeister Janee Randall Chapman Suzi McClellan Tom Smith George Berasley Candice Carter Subject ERCOT Notification Postcard Language Workshop The Notifications Postcard Language workshop will be held at the PUC Congress th floor Hearing room Gee on Thursday January th from Please be prepared to discuss language changes and the system and cost implications RSVP to me and Kyle by COB Tuesday Thanks Heidi
